                                Indoor plants have become a popular way to bring life, color, and nature into our homes. They not only enhance the decor but also improve air quality and promote a sense of well-being. However, many plant owners struggle with keeping their plants healthy and thriving. With the right knowledge and care, anyone can maintain vibrant, long-lasting indoor plants.
                            </p>
    
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Why Indoor Plants Are Worth the Effort</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Indoor plants offer numerous health benefits beyond their beauty:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
